    management: ["Observe and monitor functional cysts (most resolve in 8-12 weeks)", "Administer analgesics as ordered for pain management", "Administer oral contraceptives as prescribed to prevent new cyst formation", "Prepare for surgical intervention if torsion, rupture with hemodynamic instability, or persistent complex cyst", "Maintain NPO status if surgical intervention anticipated"],
